'''Battle plan A-seven''' was a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] combat tactic that had been developed for use by [[Twin Suns Squadron]]. It was created by the unit's co-leaders, [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] and [[Jagged Fel]], for use against the [[Yuuzhan Vong]].

